                <h1>Lollapalooza: A Must-See Music Festival</h1>
                <p>Lollapalooza is an annual music festival founded by Perry Farrell in 1991, originally as a farewell tour for his band, Jane's Addiction. Today, it features a diverse lineup of artists across multiple genres, from rock to hip-hop, and takes place in various cities worldwide. The festival is renowned for its vibrant atmosphere and cultural experiences.</p>
